Types of datatypes:
1. Hardware: reg (procedural), wire(continuous), logic (both)
2. Variable: 
   Fixed 2 state 0/1 : signed - byte, int, long int etc, unsigned - bit OR 4 state 0/1/x/z - integer, 
   Float: real
3. Simulation: time and realtime

2 state datatype: initial value is 0 and 4 state is X

%0d print 1 value
%0p all elements in array
